  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Engage in the Devil's turn-base puzzle]<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/121359615bd346dfa1d5e2f24cb4499e.poster.avif?t=1755011390\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/121359615bd346dfa1d5e2f24cb4499e.webm?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/121359615bd346dfa1d5e2f24cb4499e.mp4?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ensure your victims are as desperate as possible by giving them: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jealousy</strong>, <strong>Sadness</strong>, <strong>Delicious food</strong>, <strong>Paranoia</strong>, divine judgment, and <strong>Bad luck</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Put your victims through different stages]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-\"Break them, make them insane if you must but bring me their souls\"</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/377c5fa29079a7395aec7075d1bc8735.poster.avif?t=1755011390\" width=610 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/377c5fa29079a7395aec7075d1bc8735.webm?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/377c5fa29079a7395aec7075d1bc8735.mp4?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[What Offer would bring to the table?]</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>- ”Promise them the whole world, and make one hell of a Deal!”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/fb6c69f3cd9b71332b8f425d102361f5.poster.avif?t=1755011390\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/fb6c69f3cd9b71332b8f425d102361f5.webm?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/fb6c69f3cd9b71332b8f425d102361f5.mp4?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more desperate the victims are the less you have to offer, and the more you could ask for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Have you steel your resolve?]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-\" If not, just use your victim's resolve against them\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/01fe5cb68e21cc359f856c82bf0315de.poster.avif?t=1755011390\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/01fe5cb68e21cc359f856c82bf0315de.webm?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/01fe5cb68e21cc359f856c82bf0315de.mp4?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Losing a bet with the Grim Reaper lead you to rot in hell forever. The End.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well, it seems not even forever isn’t as long as it used to be... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since you got out with a little help, but of course, it wasn't for free.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Engage in the Devil's turn-base puzzle]<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/121359615bd346dfa1d5e2f24cb4499e.poster.avif?t=1755011390\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/121359615bd346dfa1d5e2f24cb4499e.webm?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/121359615bd346dfa1d5e2f24cb4499e.mp4?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ensure your victims are as desperate as possible by giving them: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jealousy</strong>, <strong>Sadness</strong>, <strong>Delicious food</strong>, <strong>Paranoia</strong>, divine judgment, and <strong>Bad luck</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Put your victims through different stages]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-\"Break them, make them insane if you must but bring me their souls\"</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/377c5fa29079a7395aec7075d1bc8735.poster.avif?t=1755011390\" width=610 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/377c5fa29079a7395aec7075d1bc8735.webm?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/377c5fa29079a7395aec7075d1bc8735.mp4?t=1755011390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[What Offer would bring to the table?]</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >